description: After running into a dead end with Jack, Batman's Royal Flush Gang investigation takes an unusual turn when he receives a message from Melanie Walker.
name: All In, Part 4 of 5: Pocket Tens

description: Our showstopping new event, Forever Evil continues, with more action and intrigue than ever! Just when things couldnt look any darker, three Justice Leaguers turn out to have escaped the fate of their comrades. But what can they do by themselves? Meanwhile, Lex Luthor continues to organise his fight back against the Crime Syndicate just as they start to fight among themselves! Meanwhile, two of the JLA try to escape their fate, but is it even possible?

Its non-stop action for the Dark Knight this issue, as he faces more threats than you could shake a Batarang at! In the digital-first smash Arkham Unhinged, Batman tries to rescue Catwoman from Hugo Stranges clutches, but Stranges forces are closing in! Meanwhile, in Detective Comics, Batman hunts a killer targeting Gotham Citys finest, while in Batman: The Dark Knight, the Caped Crusader battles the hypnotic Mad Hatter!

Crime never stops for Batman and his friends in the latest edition of Batman: Arkham! In this issue, Batman faces a battle to defeat his cop-killing counterpart, the Wrath! Meanwhile, in the latest instalment of Arkham Unhinged, you can witness a war between two of Gothams most nefarious residents, the Joker and the Penguin! Plus, in response to great demand, we present the start of a new run of Batwoman, beginning with the origin of Kate Kane!

Its a full-on, action-packed ride in this issue of Batman: Arkham! The chaos continues in the world of Arkham Unhinged, with appearances from The Joker, Harley Quinn, Mr. Freeze and Hugo Strange! In Detective Comics, Batman faces the Wrath in final battle! And Batwoman will need some help from someone unexpected as she tracks the scary Bloody Mary!

The battles are on in this all-action issue of Batman/Superman! In Batman/Superman itself, the Caped Crusader finds himself in opposition to a couple of unexpected foes, but whats really going on? Meanwhile, in Injustice: Gods Among Us, its time for a battle royale between the monarch of Atlantis, Aquaman, and the Justice League! And last but not least, in Superman Unchained, Superman comes up against an opponent with some very familiar abilities Wraith!

description:
Discover the universe of the Man of Steel in this jaw-dropping Superman Annual!

Soar with the Last Survivor of Krypton as he grapples with incredible villains to save the world in a selection of awesome comic strip stories! Plus- go inside Superman's base, the Fortress of Solitude, and discover all the secrets of his allies and foes!
name: ANNUAL 2014

description:
The brand new Superman Annual features a host of cool comic adventures starring the Man of Steel himself, Superman, everyone's favourite villain, Lex Luthor, and the best stories set in Metropolis.

Find out all about the Man of Steel, the planet Krypton, Superman's friends and enemies, and much more!
name: ANNUAL 2015

description:
This incredible Batman Annual is packed with Dark Knight comic strip action, with a wide selection of gripping stories involving deadly detection, colourful villains and amazing gadgets!

Also includes the origins of Batman, The Joker, Robin, Nightwing and more!
